# 🎬 StreamHub – Ultra-Fast Torrent Video Streaming App

StreamHub is a blazing-fast, ad-free, and fully responsive web application that allows users to **stream video content directly from magnet links, torrent files, or direct video URLs** in real-time — without downloading.

Built with modern technologies like **WebTorrent**, **Node.js**, and **Vite**, StreamHub is designed to deliver a seamless, buffer-free experience powered by decentralized peer-to-peer networks.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🎥 **Instant Torrent Streaming** — Paste a magnet URI and start watching immediately.
- ⏩ **Custom Video Controls** — 10s forward/back skip buttons + arrow key support.
- 📂 **Automatic File Detection** — Auto-selects video file from torrent payload.
- 📡 **Real-time Torrent Stats** — Displays download speed, peers, and file size.
- 🌓 **Dark Mode UI** — Minimal, modern, and mobile-friendly interface.
- 🌐 **CORS-enabled Express API** — Secure backend for cross-origin requests.
- 🔁 **SPA-Friendly Routing** — Built with HTML5 history support and fallback routing.

