## 🛠️ Installation & Setup

> Requires: Node.js ≥ 16.x and a modern browser with WebRTC support

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/streamhub.git
cd streamhub

# 2. Install server dependencies
cd server
npm install

# 3. Run backend server
npm run dev
# Server starts at http://localhost:3000

# 4. Start frontend (if separate Vite setup)
cd ../client
npm install
npm run dev
